Solar dataset

The dimension of Solar dataset is 5113 x 456.

First column is Date from 1994-01-01 to 2007-12-31.

Next 98 contain energy production in solar estations in units of Joules per square meter.

Finally, there are 357 columns with Principal Components that can be used as predictors.
